Package org.mcennis.graphrat.algorithm.reusablecores.instanceFactories

Interface Summary
InstanceFactory Interface for transforming Properties into Instance Objects.
 

Class Summary
DefaultInstanceFactory This class is used when an approprite Object specific factory does not exist.
DoubleArrayInstanceFactory Class for transforming double[] property values into an Instance.
DoubleInstanceFactory Class for transforming Double property values into an Instance.
InstanceFactoryRegistry Static class that holds a reference to all known factories for transforming objects to Instance objects indexed by object class.
InstanceInstanceFactory Returns the underlying instance without any modification.
IntegerInstanceFactory Class for transforming Integer property values into an Instance.
LongInstanceFactory Class for transforming Long property values into an Instance.
StringInstanceFactory Class for transforming a String into an Instance from a property of name 'name'.
